items.badge_description: It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 75 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 16.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 185 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 38!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 10 different beers with the style of IPA - New England (Imperial or Single), Pale Ale - New England or IPA - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 3!

While a pint of traditional English ale will always remain a staple, the craft beer scene in England, much like the rest of the world, has continued to grow at a rapid rate! That's 40 different beers from a brewery from England! Try 5 more for Level 9!
